Product description

TIJN Polarized Aluminum Sunglasses for Men Women Rectangular Frame UV 400 Protection - 100% Protect your eyes anywhere and give the clear and comfort vision

Product Size
Lens Width: 55mm
Frame Length: 143mm
Bridge Width: 15mm

The temples made of aluminum magnesium which has the characteristics of super lightness, excellent elasticity and durable. It enable you a longtime wearing without fatigue.

100% UV Protection
Filter out 99% of reflected glare without haze or optical distortion.
Protect your eyes and enjoy a high clarity vision more comfortably.

Suitable occasion:by motorcycle and cycling bicycle, driving, travelling, running, fishing, swimming, racing, skiing and climbing, trekking, camping, etc.
Suitable group: unisex

Tips:
-The sunglasses should be treated carefully to avoid damage and cleaned regularly.
-Clean the lens using soap water or neutral detergent, gently wipe dry with the soft glasses cloth included.
-Do not expose sunglasses to high temperatures or damp environments in a long term.

30 days quality guarantee. If there are any problems, please contact me in time

How are ratings calculated?
To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyses reviews to verify trustworthiness.
